Counter.scala: a simple counter, protected using a lock. 

LockTotalQueue.scala: a total queue, protected using a lock. 

BagOfTasksLock.scala: the concurrent objects for the trapezium example.

CounterArray.scala: an array of counters, using coarse, fine-grained, or
striped locking.

ShardedSet.scala: a set implemented using sharding.

LinkedListSet.scala: a set implemented using a linked list.

SetTest.scala: test for ShardedSet and LinkedListSet. 


Exercises
=========

ShardedMap.scala: a map implemented using sharding.

MapTest.scala: test for ShardedMap and LinkedListMap.

LinkedListMap.scala: a map implemented using a linked list.

ConcurrentIterator.scala: concurrent iterators


